<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Panel de Servicios</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d384d 0%, #2a5298 100%);
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 1rem;
        }
        header {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
        }
        .card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }
        .card h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .card p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background: white;
            color: #2a5298;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background: #2a5298;
            color: white;
        }
        footer {
            margin-top: 3rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* --- ðŸ“± RESPONSIVE PARA CEL --- */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            header h1 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }
            header p {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }
            .container {
                gap: 1rem;
            }
            .card {
                padding: 1.2rem;
            }
            .card h2 {
                font-size: 1.3rem;
            }
            .card p {
                font-size: 0.85rem;
            }
            .btn {
                padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>ðŸš¦ Panel de Servicios</h1>
        <p>Selecciona el sistema que quieres consultar</p>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="card" onclick="window.location.href='/v1/runt'">
            <h2>RUNT</h2>
            <p>Consulta de vehÃ­culos y conductores</p>
            <a class="btn" href="/v1/runt">Ir al RUNT</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card" onclick="window.location.href='/v1/login'">
            <h2>PolicÃ­a</h2>
            <p>Verifica comparendos y reportes</p>
            <a class="btn" href="/v1/login">Ir a PolicÃ­a</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>Ca colombia ER:LC TODOS LOS DERECHOS</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
